{"tid":1848542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"高級知識分子的低級思維","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T15:34:18.000Z","uid":308732,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1e54319b873e809f033f0307b60b15db44e79cf0","tid":1848542,"uid":308732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"1996年5月13日，香港頭號通緝犯葉繼歡帶著大批槍械偷渡回港，在西環登岸時遇上三個小巡警，雙方拔槍火拼，結果葉繼歡中了四槍就擒，從此半身不遂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個打刧、傷人、挾持人質、越獄等壞事做盡的賊王終於落網，市民看著他癱軟了身軀被抬上救護車那一幕，許多人都問：「這種人死有餘辜，救來幹嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「救，我們一定盡力救！」跟醫生朋友說起這件事、這想法，他們告訴我：「救傷扶危，是醫護天職，我們只是被訓練去救人，沒被訓練去殺人或者袖手旁觀。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾經聽過這說法：香港最可貴的地方，就是當你有日倒在路上，旁人會為你召救護車，救護員不管你什麼國籍、種族，第一時間會把你送院，醫院的醫護也不管你是誰、不管你口袋裏有沒有錢，盡力搶救醫治&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然而，這條美麗風景線，八個月前，忽然消失了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一場瘟疫，把香港人的醜陋表露無遺，醫護醞釀大罷工、抽生死籤照顧隔離病人、還趁火打劫要求加薪；學者專家撥火播恨，黃絲政客幸災樂禍。當年拼命救一個賊王的專業哪裡去了？沙士期間捨身救人的精神還在嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這天，醫管局宣布：「任何符合新型冠狀病毒肺炎呈報準則的患者，包括非本地人，在隔離令期間的求診和治療費用，都可獲豁免。」又引來一群政治動物撲出來發飊狂噬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府此舉，目的很清晰，就是怕有外地人因擔心要付醫療全費，明明有病都不求醫，最後引致社區播毒，情況更不受控，社會代價更大。治療費全免，就是希望把所有懷疑個案都一一集中手上，有殺錯無放過，這是防疫的方法，一般人都明都懂，然而，有些讀飽書的人卻連這個簡單道理都看不通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者沈旭暉在他臉書專頁發表鴻文，如此寫道：「危機期間，究竟香港特區政府要為多少非本地人醫療費埋單？&hellip;&hellip;任何人說『昨天發燒』，或『今朝我條氣唔順』，或『之前路過大陸醫院』，已經符合標準，前線醫生亦不能懷疑。特區政府（也就是納稅人）承擔，會獲得一條龍醫療服務&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n皇仁書院會考9A的高材生、唸過耶魯、清華、牛津等世界最高學府，教過中大、教大的沈旭暉教授&hellip;&hellip;絕頂高級知識分子了，腦袋載的竟是低級思維，計的竟是這種「婆乸」數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為一個國際關係學者，沈旭暉不是應該告訴市民，國際防疫標準該如何嗎？昨天，日本首相安倍晉三就宣佈，將新型冠狀病毒肺炎認定為日本《感染症法》中的「指定感染症」，即是說，不論國籍，所有感染者的醫療費用將由日本政府承擔。原來，由當地政府付醫療費，是國際防疫慣例。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寧多花錢也不能放過任何一個懷疑個案，這是防疫原則，老實說，如果要數浪費納稅人金錢，又幾時輪得到那些訪港內地客？香港持續八個月的黑暴，社會上單是「有形」破壞（如大學、立法會、地磚、欄杆、交通燈等）已要花21億公帑去維修，沈教授，你真的想談談「埋單」嗎？我想，大部分香港人都有興趣跟你們算算帳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原圖：大公報<br />\n作者：屈穎妍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2146d71b960928c4b31f754ce8465ddcf3918106","tid":1848542,"uid":162558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367b6b63f6902aed01ee08abcc15742b32da2bfc","tid":1848542,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾就唔理佢啦"},{"pid":"668bc1d67f09419686ce51d0c91a58d26352c76f","tid":1848542,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍緊係高級思維，佢 03 年沙士到依家都唔戴口罩架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cbc8c4f46663262b2833ed62c8abec16742c04","tid":1848542,"uid":117636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"未睇到最尾已經知係出自屈文妓之筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8a368643351df160b3e666fb9070d21c2017cd","tid":1848542,"uid":308732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"367b6b63f6902aed01ee08abcc15742b32da2bfc","tid":1848542,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾就唔理佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"睇到我好撚嬲<br />\n點解呢啲垃圾仲有人幫佢出文<br />\n幾時仆街死"},{"pid":"e8e5040ae1598d88360c2fe5ad69aba4cc257468","tid":1848542,"uid":308732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"668bc1d67f09419686ce51d0c91a58d26352c76f","tid":1848542,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍緊係高級思維，佢 03 年沙士到依家都唔戴口罩架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:46:53.000Z","msg":"原來係藍絲廢老"},{"pid":"f51ad06ee3646020eed1456601717499e09e31ce","tid":1848542,"uid":308732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5cbc8c4f46663262b2833ed62c8abec16742c04","tid":1848542,"uid":117636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"未睇到最尾已經知係出自屈文妓之筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"Ching屈機 睇嚟我真係睇得佢少"},{"pid":"472e16152258d9c25d7993119275d25d5777c5e8","tid":1848542,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"睇頭兩段已經知係屈才女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eb23d65e5cf63cc4388527aa706769835a3fb5","tid":1848542,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"668bc1d67f09419686ce51d0c91a58d26352c76f","tid":1848542,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍緊係高級思維，佢 03 年沙士到依家都唔戴口罩架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"希望佢 上次唔中 今次早 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889478ae452fb0aff31a641f1a37b99398d6dc92","tid":1848542,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"葉繼歡都未被打到頭破血流<br />\n示威者斷手斷腳被失蹤<br />\n屈文妓有冇放半個屁?"},{"pid":"c06f4452b36ad55b86aa7a59d9488a1d674e31d5","tid":1848542,"uid":259216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"好噁心呀呢篇嘢"},{"pid":"63b129b360bc99577a37274c5defba757e626699","tid":1848542,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97298110b0c8fd51812efa2729a70e1e127a6090","tid":1848542,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:00:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請幫手入去比正評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=893470fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=6ad3a18b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/?d=n<br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=4b4b6bf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=16d0ad13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=09e7359a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=8b3a9355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=cea269f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span>"},{"pid":"9589e0c3db718cd2261ce2783589c87ddf21719e","tid":1848542,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"將別人的文章扭曲，斷章取義，就係小人屈狗姸專長。<br />\n人渣藍屍寫手唔冚家剷就繼續毒害其他藍屍廢佬，其實無壞。"},{"pid":"5dd78eb5be4b8ded243a6cbafaea4ffc424f5bd2","tid":1848542,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"拉啦屌你"}